{"tid":615250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青山推VR體驗幻覺煎熬","createTime":"2018-04-03T07:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T09:14:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd8d5b957c8eb9f554af4d0c78f8f891347779d","tid":615250,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180403/20350593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F20350593&d=P4b8p5DmM7BDUOa8YOsbhG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=cea78ebe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F20350593&h=5bab8958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180403/20350593</a><br />\n<br />\n青山推VR體驗幻覺煎熬<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180403/large/03la6p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180403%2Flarge%2F03la6p4.jpg&h=a8a4a4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蕭慧敏（右）盼活動令參觀者對患者產生同理心。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大眾對精神病的負面標籤，是患者康復和融入社會的障礙。青山醫院擬於明年中開設精神健康體驗館，透過VR虛擬實境等技術，模擬精神病患者受幻聽和視覺幻覺煎熬，再由康復者親身分享經歷。青山醫院精神健康學院執委會聯席主席蕭慧敏說，過往研究證實親身接觸有助消除歧視，盼上述環節令參觀者對患者有同理心，以及增加他們對精神病認知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n了解康復者真實經歷<br />\n<br />\n青山醫院本身設歷史文物館，新計劃於原址改建成精神健康體驗館。青山及小欖醫院護理部總經理梅杏春說，體驗館將設5個展區，包括精神科治療發展史、展示患者腦部病變情況、現今治療方式、病徵體驗及介紹抗壓知識的精神健康資訊站。<br />\n<br />\n梅說，團隊與康復者訪談，了解他們的真實經歷，體驗館其中一個情境來自精神分裂症患者，他在家看金像獎頒獎禮電視直播時，突然有聲音恭賀他獲獎，隨即又有另一把聲音警告他不要離家，否則會被妒忌他的人打死。患者初時以為「鬼上身」沒求醫，但疑神疑鬼下不敢外出，失眠，失去工作之餘，更與家人關係破裂。梅說，體驗後會由康復者親身分享，盼參觀者可感受患者的困擾。<br />\n蕭慧敏說，本港每6個人就有1人有出現精神問題的風險，當中部份人確診精神病，發病率與國際相若。社會對精神病仍有負面定型，患者難融入社會。<br />\n<br />\n體驗館獲匯豐150周年慈善計劃資助3,000萬元，料明年中開幕，免費入場。梅杏春說，估計每年1.6萬人次參觀，會主動接觸學校安排參觀及導賞，另舉辦心理教育講座。<br />\n■記者袁樂婷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180403/large/03la6p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180403%2Flarge%2F03la6p2.jpg&h=6ecbad7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昔日病房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180403/large/03la6p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180403%2Flarge%2F03la6p3.jpg&h=a261ade0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVR體驗室<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180403/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180403%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=f662efa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9c6eb16ea885ab0407177364e3aac82cfdfdf09","tid":615250,"uid":156363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"冇病變有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72f75f345a8b08c5ebfecdf361e06a0ce1eaadd","tid":615250,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:02:59.000Z","msg":"outlast？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042b530fbbeeeedf695f235d09674a2806ad273c","tid":615250,"uid":102880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1f716015b3f29993b77e91147a7eb053f870c3","tid":615250,"uid":818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"outlast 真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\